1
00:01:36,727 --> 00:01:40,246
[Episode 31]

2
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:47,940
Indeed. We haven't seen this happen for years.

3
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:56,199
Let's go take a look.

4
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:58,199
I'll keep an eye on Zhao Zheng De.

5
00:02:02,199 --> 00:02:03,239
Hey, make way.

6
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,719
Make way, please.

7
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:06,565
Lord Zhan.

8
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,999
This is Wang Qing's brother, Wang Heng.

9
00:02:12,999 --> 00:02:14,440
Wang Heng?

10
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,934
I know these clothes.

11
00:02:15,934 --> 00:02:18,400
They were newly made in my shop.

12
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:21,062
- No wonder.
- It's Wang Heng, no doubt.

13
00:02:21,062 --> 00:02:23,040
It's been a while since I saw him.

14
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:26,190
- I haven't seen him lately.
- Exactly.

15
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,720
I've been dealing with the
Xiuluo Sect for many years.

16
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:50,487
I'm so familiar with it.

17
00:02:50,487 --> 00:02:54,959
It seems they've made a comeback
to Wanshan County.

18
00:02:54,959 --> 00:02:57,840
About Wang Qing's case, did we overthink it?

19
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:01,440
It might really be the work of the Xiuluo Sect.

20
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,840
Right

21
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,239
when we started doubting the old cases,

22
00:03:05,239 --> 00:03:08,650
the Xiuluo Sect struck again.

23
00:03:08,650 --> 00:03:12,000
It feels like they're trying to cover it up.

24
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,537
You have a point.

25
00:03:14,537 --> 00:03:18,300
Did you find any clues in Gucheng County?

26
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,280
We brought someone back.

27
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:26,720
He is related to the case
involving Jin Niang's husband ten years ago.

28
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:30,082
Right now, we need a place to settle him.

29
00:03:30,082 --> 00:03:31,240
I understand.

30
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,720
This man must not enter my county court.

31
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:36,159
Don't mention those clues

32
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:38,239
from Wanshan County there, either.

33
00:03:38,239 --> 00:03:42,762
So you're sure there's a spy in your court?

34
00:03:48,239 --> 00:03:49,640
On the day Zhong Shou was killed,

35
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:52,119
I checked everyone's whereabouts in the court.

36
00:03:52,119 --> 00:03:54,439
He was supposed to go to the
neighboring county to deliver documents,

37
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:57,480
but he handed the task off to someone else.

38
00:03:57,480 --> 00:04:00,320
Also checked the jail's shift rotation.

39
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:02,320
That day, outside Qiu Han's house,

40
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:04,239
we ran into Zhong Shou.

41
00:04:04,239 --> 00:04:08,239
It was Zhu Ming Yuan who distracted us.

42
00:04:08,239 --> 00:04:10,360
Lord Zhan.

43
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:13,240
It's at the corner ahead.

44
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,760
If that's the case,

45
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:20,200
Luo Chang Shui murdered Zhong Shou,
likely on Zhu Ming Yuan's orders.

46
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,960
That would explain why Zhu Ming Yuan

47
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:26,040
killed Luo Chang Shui in front of everyone.

48
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,279
He did it to silence him.

49
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:29,040
I was so blind.

50
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:32,880
I let this thorn stay under my nose
for so many years.

51
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,160
Do you need our help?

52
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,360
No need.

53
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,479
Now that we know his identity,

54
00:04:37,479 --> 00:04:39,959
he's out in the open. We're in the shadows.

55
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,679
Let's see if we can use him.

56
00:04:41,679 --> 00:04:44,959
Find out what his Lord is plotting
in Wanshan County.

57
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:46,679
There's a vacant house on Wansheng Street.

58
00:04:46,679 --> 00:04:47,720
It should be safe.

59
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,560
Have Bai take him there first.

60
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:52,120
The three of us will lure Zhu Ming Yuan
back to the court.

61
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,440
When it gets dark,

62
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:55,320
we'll meet up with Bai.

63
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,737
Let's do that.

64
00:05:06,614 --> 00:05:08,479
Mr. Zhao, are you itching for a beating?

65
00:05:08,479 --> 00:05:10,809
How about I give you a few needles?

66
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,040
Hurry up and tidy up.

67
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,359
There are no servants here
for you to order around.

68
00:05:15,359 --> 00:05:19,662
If you can't finish it,
you'll sleep on the floor tonight.

69
00:05:53,025 --> 00:05:55,612
Zhao Zheng De?

70
00:05:55,612 --> 00:05:58,175
Why did you bring him here?

71
00:06:01,012 --> 00:06:03,160
The youth disappearance case in Gucheng County

72
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,920
is related to Zhao Yue An.

73
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,079
Ten years ago,

74
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:08,079
he killed Jin Niang to silence her.

75
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:10,039
Once we find Zhao Yue An,

76
00:06:10,039 --> 00:06:11,680
the truth behind the case

77
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:14,320
will come to light.

78
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:17,320
- Isn't Zhao Yue An already--
- Zhao Yue An isn't dead.

79
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:21,120
That brat used a fake death trick
and fooled all of you.

80
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,079
But that's not the best part.

81
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:25,040
Lord of Xiangyang, that old rogue,

82
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,680
had a son out of wedlock
and kept it from his wives.

83
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,920
But he didn't dare raise him,

84
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,279
nor did he dare bring him home.

85
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:32,760
So he fostered him
at the home of this foster father.

86
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:37,275
Zhao Yue An
is the Lord of Xiangyang's illegitimate son.

87
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:41,600
So you want to take Zhao Zheng De

88
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,978
to identify Zhao Yue An.

89
00:06:46,639 --> 00:06:48,760
Taking him there...

90
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,440
isn't it unsafe?

91
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:52,240
If the Lord of Xiangyang finds out,

92
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:55,000
he'll do everything he can to eliminate him.

93
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,639
Hu has a point.

94
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:57,920
Better to bring the suspects here.

95
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:01,648
This is Hu's territory, so it'll be safer.

96
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,160
If we plan ahead while we're here,

97
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,815
won't it be easier to capture him?

98
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:09,966
Do you have any suspects in mind?

99
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:18,000
No need to bring all three of them, right?

100
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,120
Just bringing Shao Ji Zu over.

101
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,960
Since there are three suspects,

102
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:24,199
why only bring one?

103
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:27,637
It's unlikely that Zhao Yue An
is either of the other two.

104
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,599
Of those two,

105
00:07:30,599 --> 00:07:32,800
one is Ling Long's close friend,

106
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,280
and the other is

107
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,800
her elder brother.

108
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:38,320
Even if it's unlikely, they're still suspects.

109
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:40,399
The lead on Zhao Yue An was hard to come by.

110
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:41,839
If we're arranging an identification,

111
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:45,199
we must ensure all three are present.

112
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:47,480
Magistrate Hu, is that really necessary?

113
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:50,000
- We've dealt with Shao Ji Zu--
- Bai.

114
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,639
I understand the bond you've shared,

115
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:54,519
and Miss Huo's dilemma.

116
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,760
But right now, we cannot let emotions rule us.

117
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,120
If I were like you,

118
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,720
then Zhu Ming Yuan, that spy,

119
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:03,079
would stay in my court forever.

120
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:05,000
Hu is right.

121
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,839
I'll find a way to get all three of them here.

122
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:10,440
Only by proving my brother and Tang
are not Zhao Yue An,

123
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:13,762
can I truly set my mind at ease.

124
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:18,120
I was planning to invite Tang over
to study needle techniques with me.

125
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:20,279
I'll just write him a letter.

126
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:22,199
Two out of the three will suffice.

127
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:24,399
If it's not those two, then it's Huo Feng.

128
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:27,162
We can discuss by then. What do you think?

129
00:08:27,162 --> 00:08:28,480
Oh, come on.

130
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,079
Listen to me. It's settled.

131
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:32,440
Huo Xiao Mei, write a letter to Shao Ji Zu.

132
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:35,199
Tell him to come over to discuss the marriage.

133
00:08:35,199 --> 00:08:36,959
Shao Ji Zu is a cautious man.

134
00:08:36,959 --> 00:08:38,519
I'm afraid he won't fall for it.

135
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,839
Let's give it a try.

136
00:08:39,839 --> 00:08:42,725
Where should we meet?

137
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:50,000
How about we meet him in the Heaven suite
on the second floor of Juxian Pavilion?

138
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,760
That room is directly across from
the second-floor lobby of Wanxing Restaurant.

139
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,839
As long as the window is open,

140
00:08:53,839 --> 00:08:57,737
we can see everything inside the room.

141
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:45,370
[Zhou Ji Liang, Master of Xiuluo Cult]

142
00:09:48,719 --> 00:09:50,079
These days,

143
00:09:50,079 --> 00:09:52,435
people in Wanshan County

144
00:09:52,435 --> 00:09:54,839
has been buzzing about the murders.

145
00:09:54,839 --> 00:09:57,780
Everyone is in a panic.

146
00:09:59,079 --> 00:10:03,096
I haven't felt this satisfied in a long time.

147
00:10:04,362 --> 00:10:06,599
By the way,

148
00:10:06,599 --> 00:10:09,440
the people who are slated to die next,

149
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,294
can I use them to test my poisons?

150
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,157
Nonsense!

151
00:10:16,402 --> 00:10:19,680
Do you think we planned all this

152
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:23,080
just so you could slaughter the innocent?

153
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,559
I don't care what your plan is.

154
00:10:25,559 --> 00:10:28,480
Mine is to slaughter the innocent.

155
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,679
No.

156
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,360
Using poison...

157
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,639
will leave traces.

158
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:38,360
You'd better stick to the plan.

159
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,000
In the coming days,

160
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:43,900
I will help you settle this.

161
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:52,279
You're helping me out of kindness?

162
00:10:52,279 --> 00:10:54,880
Is Zhan Zhao pressing you too hard?

163
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:58,125
You can't stay in the county court?

164
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:03,100
He is indeed pressing me.

165
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:07,880
But once this move of yours is played,

166
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:11,437
it'll keep him quiet for a while.

167
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,760
Zhan Zhao.

168
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:19,679
It's been ten years.

169
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:23,512
We're finally going to meet.

170
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:29,559
Why do we have to travel at night?

171
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:33,760
If you ask me,
we should stay at the county inn tonight.

172
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:36,120
I'm in a hurry to sell the goods.

173
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,799
What, don't you want a good price?

174
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:39,550
I'm not going.

175
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:42,399
We're in the middle of nowhere. Too scary!

176
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:45,662
What if we run into wild animals?
There's nowhere to hide.

177
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,439
Fine.

178
00:11:47,439 --> 00:11:49,279
You're such a burden.

179
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:51,240
You...

180
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,639
There's light over there.

181
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:54,840
Let's see if we can rest there.

182
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,762
Let's go.

183
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:07,960
W-What's going on here?

184
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,799
Could it be the work of an evil cult?

185
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:13,162
I'm afraid so.

186
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:55,919
[Wanshan Country Court]
Murder! Murder! Murder!

187
00:12:55,919 --> 00:12:58,240
Murder!

188
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,600
We want to report!

189
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:02,960
Open the door! Open up!

190
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,039
Another case.

191
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:06,600
It's Liu San Lang's family.

192
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:09,960
Three more are dead.

193
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:12,159
Who on earth is the new master
of the Xiuluo Sect?

194
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:14,080
How can he be so heartless?

195
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,465
After Mo Dao died,

196
00:13:15,465 --> 00:13:18,480
the Xiuluo Sect completely vanished.

197
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,080
As for this new master,

198
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,880
there hasn't been a single rumor.

199
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:26,120
So their killings are meant to tell us
they did all the previous cases?

200
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:28,279
This is far too crude.

201
00:13:28,279 --> 00:13:31,039
But the previous victims were all young men.

202
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:32,259
This time,

203
00:13:32,259 --> 00:13:33,919
Liu San Lang's parents were also killed.

204
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:36,360
Why would they change their targets?

205
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,840
For now,

206
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:40,080
the Xiuluo Sect's motive remains unclear.

207
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,319
But since they serve the Lord of Xiangyang,

208
00:13:42,319 --> 00:13:43,865
they

209
00:13:43,865 --> 00:13:45,720
must be trying to thwart our investigation.

210
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:48,279
Once we find Zhao Yue An and uncover the truth,

211
00:13:48,279 --> 00:13:52,439
the Xiuluo Sect's killings here
will naturally cease.

212
00:13:52,439 --> 00:13:53,513
Ling Long,

213
00:13:53,513 --> 00:13:54,812
Has Shao Ji Zu replied?

214
00:13:54,812 --> 00:13:56,840
Yeah. He agreed.

215
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,120
Just like that?

216
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,279
That was too easy.

217
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,559
Could it be a trap?

218
00:14:00,559 --> 00:14:03,300
We should be cautious.

219
00:14:08,799 --> 00:14:10,319
Zhan, long time no see.

220
00:14:10,319 --> 00:14:11,360
Long time no see.

221
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,559
You arrived so quickly.

222
00:14:12,559 --> 00:14:13,880
Did you miss us?

223
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,919
I missed you all.

224
00:14:15,919 --> 00:14:18,712
- Come on.
- Bai.

225
00:14:18,712 --> 00:14:20,240
- Come here.
- Zhan.

226
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,325
This way.

227
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,177
This is...

228
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:38,000
See? I told you it wasn't him.

229
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,240
Tang.

230
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,250
I'm sorry.

231
00:14:40,250 --> 00:14:41,840
Inviting you here this time...

232
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:45,125
wasn't just for the needle technique.

233
00:15:16,712 --> 00:15:19,025
Sir, what would you like to buy?

234
00:15:19,025 --> 00:15:21,737
Give me some plums.

235
00:15:21,737 --> 00:15:23,639
Hey. Why are you here?

236
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:26,120
You're asking? I came here looking for you.

237
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,960
Why did you sneak out behind my back again?

238
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,960
Wanshan County has been dangerous lately.
Stop running out alone.

239
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:33,480
I come to buy you something delicious, okay?

240
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,760
- Let's go.
- Why plums again?

241
00:15:35,760 --> 00:15:37,559
You don't need to buy them every day.

242
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:39,240
We haven't finished the left ones.

243
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:40,840
These are delicious.

244
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,319
But they'll cause heatiness.

245
00:15:42,319 --> 00:15:43,519
Fine.

246
00:15:43,519 --> 00:15:46,240
Friends should be honest with each other.

247
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,960
But as it concerns the case,

248
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:50,399
we didn't dare tell you the truth.

249
00:15:50,399 --> 00:15:52,880
After weighing it, we took this course.

250
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:56,039
We handled this poorly.

251
00:15:56,039 --> 00:15:57,439
We owe you an apology.

252
00:15:57,439 --> 00:15:59,625
I'm sorry, Tang.

253
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:04,000
I even wrote the address in the letter.
Don't you understand?

254
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,840
I have always trusted you.

255
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:10,519
I know you did it for the Imperial Court.
It's just...

256
00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:13,679
It's just that you mistook me for
the Lord of Xiangyang's illegitimate son.

257
00:16:13,679 --> 00:16:15,439
That's too ridiculous and outrageous!

258
00:16:15,439 --> 00:16:17,399
I feel wronged on behalf of my late father.

259
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:20,159
I won't let you off easily.

260
00:16:20,159 --> 00:16:21,200
You!

261
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:23,480
When this is over, you must grill fish for me.

262
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:26,159
At least three, as an apology!

263
00:16:26,159 --> 00:16:28,840
And you. Didn't you contact
the Baihua Sect for the antidote?

264
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:32,159
I have to be the first one to know the formula.

265
00:16:32,159 --> 00:16:34,279
Fine.

266
00:16:35,279 --> 00:16:36,439
As for you.

267
00:16:36,439 --> 00:16:40,062
Quick. Let me check your pulse as an apology.

268
00:16:55,639 --> 00:16:57,600
How is it?

269
00:17:00,319 --> 00:17:01,720
Before we left Xiangyang,

270
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:05,000
Bai copied
a Heavenly Root Moon Cave manual for me.

271
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,840
I've been studying it every day
and have made some progress.

272
00:17:07,840 --> 00:17:11,559
This technique might temporarily suppress
the poison in him,

273
00:17:11,559 --> 00:17:13,760
buying us more time to find the cure.

274
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:15,679
- Really?
- Really.

275
00:17:15,679 --> 00:17:18,960
But there are still a few points

276
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:21,919
- that I haven't figured out.
- I have a few questions too.

277
00:17:21,919 --> 00:17:25,275
Good thing you're here. Let's figure it out.

278
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:34,439
Was what you said just now true?

279
00:17:34,439 --> 00:17:37,313
Actually, I'm not entirely sure yet.
We can only try.

280
00:17:37,313 --> 00:17:39,880
We should hurry and figure out
the needle technique,

281
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:41,279
so we can treat him soon.

282
00:17:41,279 --> 00:17:43,319
Otherwise, if we delay any longer...

283
00:17:43,319 --> 00:17:45,439
- I think--
- Even forgot the medical book.

284
00:17:45,439 --> 00:17:47,899
What are you two discussing?

285
00:17:48,639 --> 00:17:51,200
I just discussed it with Tang.

286
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:54,360
He'll go with you tomorrow as your family
to meet Shao Ji Zu.

287
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:57,240
Yes. Bai has already told me.
I'll protect you tomorrow.

288
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,960
I won't let you be mistreated.

289
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:03,312
You're so guilty you forgot I have
The Silent World Within Earshotâ€‹?

290
00:18:05,159 --> 00:18:07,439
Alright. Go study your needle technique.
Don't delay.

291
00:18:07,439 --> 00:18:10,462
Yes, no time to waste. Let's go.

292
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:32,137
Come in.

293
00:18:41,839 --> 00:18:43,160
Commander Shao.

294
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,737
What is it?

295
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:48,440
Commander Shao,
are you going to Wanshan for the meeting?

296
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,559
- Yes.
- I don't think it's wise.

297
00:18:50,559 --> 00:18:52,799
This is clearly a trap set by the other side.

298
00:18:52,799 --> 00:18:54,400
You shouldn't go.

299
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,559
Do you think I can't see through it?

300
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:59,987
I'm just worried about your safety.

301
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,720
There's less than half a month left

302
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:15,902
until the wedding day.

303
00:19:16,537 --> 00:19:18,680
You think...

304
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:21,160
the bride...

305
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:23,852
has never even tried on her wedding dress,

306
00:19:23,852 --> 00:19:25,279
does that make sense?

307
00:19:25,279 --> 00:19:26,559
Commander Shao,

308
00:19:26,559 --> 00:19:28,879
so you want to bring Miss Ling Long back?

309
00:19:28,879 --> 00:19:31,360
I'll pick some elite soldiers,
disguise them as civilians,

310
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:32,599
and send them into the city.

311
00:19:32,599 --> 00:19:34,212
No need.

312
00:19:34,799 --> 00:19:37,450
Just prepare a fast horse for me.

313
00:19:38,119 --> 00:19:40,560
Dong Jun doesn't care about anyone

314
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:43,238
except for His Lordship.

315
00:19:43,879 --> 00:19:46,225
I'd like to see...

316
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:50,900
what he's capable of tomorrow.

317
00:19:58,319 --> 00:19:59,799
- Here, boss.
- Here, take it.

318
00:19:59,799 --> 00:20:01,975
Thank you.

319
00:20:21,687 --> 00:20:25,337
[Juxian Pavilion]

320
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:10,879
This is the room Miss Huo booked.

321
00:21:10,879 --> 00:21:12,279
We cleaned it up early.

322
00:21:12,279 --> 00:21:13,920
The tea and snacks are all ready.

323
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:16,079
Bring another set of teacups.

324
00:21:16,079 --> 00:21:17,887
Okay.

325
00:21:26,170 --> 00:21:27,627
How is it?

326
00:21:27,627 --> 00:21:28,720
We've checked.

327
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:30,960
There's no ambush on this street.

328
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,680
Did I underestimate Shao Ji Zu?

329
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:35,387
He actually dares to come alone.

330
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,720
We'll go up first.

331
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,160
Be careful.

332
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,720
Tang, take care of her.

333
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:42,737
Don't worry.

334
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,079
When Magistrate Hu first took office,

335
00:21:59,079 --> 00:22:01,359
the Xiuluo Sect was much wilder than this.

336
00:22:01,359 --> 00:22:02,839
Didn't he settle it in the end?

337
00:22:02,839 --> 00:22:05,000
Then why is he helpless this time?

338
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,039
What do you know?

339
00:22:06,039 --> 00:22:09,160
The Xiuluo Sect is not killing
for some cult ritual.

340
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:11,475
Magistrate Hu can't drive them away this time.

341
00:22:11,475 --> 00:22:13,799
Spilling it! Just tell us!

342
00:22:13,799 --> 00:22:15,519
I wouldn't dare.

343
00:22:15,519 --> 00:22:18,451
If I speak recklessly...

344
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:22,202
the Xiuluo Sect will come after me.

345
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:25,440
Waiter, another bowl of noodles!

346
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:27,839
And a few more dishes. Put it on my tab.

347
00:22:27,839 --> 00:22:29,960
- Coming right up!
- I'll take him away.

348
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,950
You stay here.

349
00:22:48,427 --> 00:22:50,420
Now that the Tang Sect has fallen,
you, their loser of a master,

350
00:22:50,420 --> 00:22:52,240
have plenty of time.

351
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,760
This is about my marriage to Ling Long.
Why are you butting in?

352
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,319
Watch your mouth!

353
00:22:56,319 --> 00:22:57,840
The Tang Sect's downfall

354
00:22:57,840 --> 00:23:00,521
was all thanks to you and Si Ming.

355
00:23:00,521 --> 00:23:02,160
What you owe us,

356
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:04,775
I will settle with you sooner or later.

357
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,559
If you really had the ability,

358
00:23:07,559 --> 00:23:10,320
you wouldn't have been so pathetic...

359
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:13,143
that you couldn't even avenge your uncle.

360
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:21,166
Ling Long, have a seat.

361
00:23:24,599 --> 00:23:26,375
Sit.

362
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,400
Who else is coming?

363
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:39,279
This marriage isn't something we can settle.

364
00:23:39,279 --> 00:23:40,879
Wait a moment.

365
00:23:40,879 --> 00:23:43,150
He'll be here soon.

366
00:24:05,839 --> 00:24:07,640
Would you two like to hear a song?

367
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:09,987
No, thank you.

368
00:24:14,039 --> 00:24:17,160
- Sir, would you like to hear a song?
- No, no, no.

369
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:19,519
Would you two like to hear a song?

370
00:24:19,519 --> 00:24:22,440
- No, no.
- These people still have the nerve to stay.

371
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:24,079
So many people have died already.

372
00:24:24,079 --> 00:24:27,503
Any longer, and who knows what might happen.

373
00:24:41,079 --> 00:24:42,400
Why is he here?

374
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,599
Sir.

375
00:24:43,599 --> 00:24:45,740
Would you two like to hear a song?

376
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:46,960
Go away!

377
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:49,650
You're ruining my mood!

378
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,599
Sir, you...

379
00:24:53,599 --> 00:24:56,079
Careful, careful, careful.

380
00:24:56,079 --> 00:24:58,400
Excuse me, excuse me.

381
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,900
Pardon me.

382
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:02,037
Pardon me.

383
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:13,262
Come in.

384
00:25:18,319 --> 00:25:20,240
- Brother.
- Huo.

385
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:22,200
Ling Long.

386
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:27,879
You rejected me many times before.

387
00:25:27,879 --> 00:25:30,480
I tried everything, but nothing worked.

388
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:32,873
So I could only ask your brother...

389
00:25:32,873 --> 00:25:34,720
to come and talk to you.

390
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:37,520
Huo, please.

391
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:58,079
Do you remember what San Lang said on the day

392
00:25:58,079 --> 00:25:59,825
they examined Liu Er Lang's body?

393
00:25:59,825 --> 00:26:01,240
He did say something.

394
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:05,160
He said his brother was killed
by the Xiuluo Sect.

395
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:08,240
- That's it.
- You mean revenge?

396
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:10,480
But didn't Wang Heng flee
in the middle of the night?

397
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:12,240
He never identified the Xiuluo Sect.

398
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:15,960
Wang Heng fled to a relative's house
in the neighboring county that night.

399
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:17,920
When they asked about his brother's death,

400
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:19,480
he said the same thing as San Lang.

401
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,880
My aunt is in that county.

402
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,559
She told me herself.

403
00:26:22,559 --> 00:26:25,000
Doesn't that mean none of us can escape?

404
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,680
I never reported my family's case.

405
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:29,187
- I also--
- Stop talking.

406
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:41,079
Ling Long. After you left home,

407
00:26:41,079 --> 00:26:43,119
Father wrote several letters
to the Lord of Xiangyang,

408
00:26:43,119 --> 00:26:44,680
but they were all returned.

409
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:46,839
He even went to Xiangyang in person.

410
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:48,319
Paid a visit to His Lordship.

411
00:26:48,319 --> 00:26:49,600
But he only sent back

412
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:52,440
a box of treasures.

413
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,950
He said it was an additional
betrothal gift for you.

414
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:57,279
The Lord of Xiangyang's stance is very clear.

415
00:26:57,279 --> 00:26:58,760
Regarding this marriage,

416
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:00,000
our Huo family...

417
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:02,279
has no choice but to accept.

418
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:08,039
Whether a marriage proceeds or not
should be voluntary.

419
00:27:08,039 --> 00:27:12,279
I have never heard of a matchmaker
who insists on forcing people.

420
00:27:12,279 --> 00:27:14,319
- The Lord of Xiangyang--
- Huo.

421
00:27:14,319 --> 00:27:17,400
Saying it like that won't move Ling Long.

422
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:20,575
She didn't care about parental orders,
matchmakers,

423
00:27:20,575 --> 00:27:22,879
or His Lordship's arranged proposal.

424
00:27:22,879 --> 00:27:25,039
So why exactly is she marrying me?

425
00:27:25,039 --> 00:27:27,170
Brother, you...

426
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:31,812
You have to tell Ling Long the truth.

427
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:38,712
What truth?

428
00:27:53,287 --> 00:27:56,700
[Juxian Pavilion]

429
00:28:10,359 --> 00:28:11,520
Huo Feng is here.

430
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:13,640
He just went in.

431
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:17,975
Strange.
The three of them are gathered together.

432
00:28:21,279 --> 00:28:22,440
[Juxian Pavilion]
Shao Ji Zu.

433
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:25,160
You should have understood
what I meant just now.

434
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:29,119
Since our family has accepted this marriage,

435
00:28:29,119 --> 00:28:31,240
don't cause any more complications.

436
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:33,680
Complications?

437
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:36,879
Shouldn't Ling Long know
why she's getting married?

438
00:28:36,879 --> 00:28:38,359
Shouldn't she know...

439
00:28:38,359 --> 00:28:41,337
the truth of this matter?

440
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:46,327
What on earth does he mean?

441
00:28:48,845 --> 00:28:50,571
Ling Long,

442
00:28:51,279 --> 00:28:53,599
actually, you've been mistaken about one thing.

443
00:28:53,599 --> 00:28:55,840
You think this marriage alliance

444
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:58,319
is for your Linglong Eye.

445
00:28:58,319 --> 00:29:00,039
But that's not the case.

446
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:02,039
I'm not the only one with an agenda.

447
00:29:02,039 --> 00:29:03,240
Me,

448
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,920
His Lordship,

449
00:29:04,920 --> 00:29:07,519
and your Huo family.

450
00:29:07,519 --> 00:29:11,387
We are just getting what we need.

451
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,400
[Juxian Pavilion]
Do you think their talk fell through?

452
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:19,240
There's been no sound for so long.

453
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:21,700
Should we go help them out?

454
00:29:33,050 --> 00:29:35,359
Ling Long,

455
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,640
you're usually quite clever.

456
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:41,359
Why are you so dull...

457
00:29:41,359 --> 00:29:43,760
when it comes to your own affairs?

458
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:45,920
Have you wondered,

459
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:49,160
why did His Lordship

460
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:51,760
choose your family specifically?

461
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:57,760
And why he's pushing so hard
for our two families to unite?

462
00:30:03,826 --> 00:30:04,839
Huo.

463
00:30:04,839 --> 00:30:06,160
Let's discuss it later.

464
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,599
I'll take her back.

465
00:30:07,599 --> 00:30:08,599
Ling Long, let's go.

466
00:30:08,599 --> 00:30:09,760
Huo Ling Long.

467
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:12,839
I know how you feel about Zhan Zhao.

468
00:30:12,839 --> 00:30:15,362
But you are a Huo.

469
00:30:15,362 --> 00:30:18,160
You're destined to never be
on the same path as Zhan Zhao.

470
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:20,359
I've tried to advise you many times.

471
00:30:20,359 --> 00:30:23,400
I told you not to investigate with him,
but you wouldn't listen.

472
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:26,200
You're the one who drove yourself
into a corner.

473
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:29,240
You're the one
who drove the Huo family into a dead end.

474
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:31,842
Shao Ji Zu, shut up!

475
00:30:32,562 --> 00:30:34,079
[Juxian Pavilion]

476
00:30:34,079 --> 00:30:35,559
They really did fall through.

477
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:37,925
Why start fighting?

478
00:30:48,392 --> 00:30:49,962
[Juxian Pavilion]

479
00:30:57,079 --> 00:30:59,300
You recognized him?

480
00:31:02,112 --> 00:31:04,625
[Juxian Pavilion]

481
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:16,275
Is the one in white Zhao Yue An?

482
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:22,723
This 'Hongmen Banquet' is truly lively.

483
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,640
[Wanxing Restaurant]
Huo,

484
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:28,319
since you don't want me to tell the truth,

485
00:31:28,319 --> 00:31:31,319
stay here and talk in detail.

486
00:31:32,319 --> 00:31:33,720
Ling Long,

487
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,440
the wedding date is near.

488
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:38,512
I'll be waiting for you at the Shao Mansion.

489
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,480
[Wanxing Restaurant]
Tell me!

490
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:54,012
Was the one who left Zhao Yue An? Was it?

491
00:32:00,279 --> 00:32:01,702
No.

492
00:32:02,599 --> 00:32:04,625
It wasn't him.

493
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:08,520
He is Yue An.

494
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:16,455
Huo Feng.

495
00:32:24,507 --> 00:32:26,502
What should we do?

496
00:33:22,739 --> 00:33:25,050
Soul-Chasing Nails!

497
00:33:25,050 --> 00:33:27,637
You're from the Xiuluo Sect.

498
00:33:30,079 --> 00:33:32,475
Go stop Shao Ji Zu.

499
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:10,415
Xiao Chen, watch them.

500
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:16,559
The people of Wanshan County are so innocent!

501
00:35:16,559 --> 00:35:20,387
How could they die at the hands of
villainous accomplices like you?

502
00:35:44,879 --> 00:35:48,125
- The Xiuluo Sect is here!
- The Xiuluo Sect is here!

503
00:35:57,341 --> 00:35:59,012
Zhan Zhao.

504
00:35:59,012 --> 00:36:01,637
Do you still remember me?

505
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:23,888
You're late.

506
00:36:23,888 --> 00:36:25,879
I made my move before you this time.

507
00:36:25,879 --> 00:36:27,560
So it was you impersonating me.

508
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:30,319
Don't be angry. I am you.

509
00:36:30,319 --> 00:36:32,319
You and I are not enemies.

510
00:36:32,319 --> 00:36:35,360
Besides, you should give that title to me.

511
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:38,840
I'm more suited to be the Yaksha than you.

512
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:44,520
Zhou Ji Liang?

513
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:46,799
What?

514
00:36:46,799 --> 00:36:49,760
You didn't expect the new master
of the Xiuluo Sect...

515
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:52,120
to be your old acquaintance, did you?

516
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:55,080
The murders in Wanshan County these days...

517
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:57,640
were all my handiwork.

518
00:36:57,640 --> 00:36:59,440
Well?

519
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,351
Was it spectacular?

520
00:37:01,351 --> 00:37:03,360
Why did you kill so many people?

521
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:05,080
Killing people...

522
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:06,839
does it require a reason?

523
00:37:06,839 --> 00:37:08,680
It's been ten years, Zhan Zhao.

524
00:37:08,680 --> 00:37:10,012
You've changed.

525
00:37:10,012 --> 00:37:13,815
But me and my two bloodthirsty blades

526
00:37:13,815 --> 00:37:16,574
have never changed.

527
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:33,720
Didn't you get poisoned by
Old Souls at First Glance?

528
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:36,900
Yet your power hasn't decreased at all.

529
00:38:17,422 --> 00:38:18,955
My dear! My dear!

530
00:38:18,955 --> 00:38:20,160
- My dear!
- Don't come over!

531
00:38:20,160 --> 00:38:21,360
Give me Zhao Zheng De.

532
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,480
Hurry!

533
00:39:02,955 --> 00:39:04,640
You're heavily poisoned,

534
00:39:04,640 --> 00:39:06,399
yet you're still trying so hard to catch me.

535
00:39:06,399 --> 00:39:11,475
What a pity.
Wanshan people won't appreciate you.

536
00:39:11,475 --> 00:39:13,525
By the way,

537
00:39:13,525 --> 00:39:16,520
the Ming boy is still with you, right?

538
00:39:16,520 --> 00:39:19,560
I haven't seen him today. Kind of pity.

539
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:21,800
I do miss him.

540
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:25,200
Who is the murderer
who killed his entire family?

541
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:28,225
Did you tell him the truth?

542
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,895
Zhu Ming Yuan! Let him go.

543
00:39:47,895 --> 00:39:50,319
I'll let you leave.

544
00:39:50,319 --> 00:39:51,720
If I want to leave,

545
00:39:51,720 --> 00:39:54,000
none of you can stop me.

546
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,879
That's not a good deal.

547
00:39:55,879 --> 00:39:58,537
Hand Zhao Zheng De over.

548
00:39:58,537 --> 00:40:00,880
Then I'll let him go.

549
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:03,880
Do you hear me? Give me Zhao Zheng De!

550
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:06,560
Lord Hu! Please save my husband!

551
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,160
Please save him!

552
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:10,120
Lord Hu.

553
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:12,600
This Zhao man isn't even from our county.

554
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:14,760
Just listen to him and make the trade.

555
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:15,839
We can't trade him.

556
00:40:15,839 --> 00:40:18,680
Zhao Zheng De is an important witness
in Lord Zhan's case.

557
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:19,720
He must not be harmed.

558
00:40:19,720 --> 00:40:21,880
Zhan Zhao, it's Zhan Zhao again!

559
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:24,933
All the troubles here were caused by him!

560
00:40:24,933 --> 00:40:26,959
Exactly! What damn witness?

561
00:40:26,959 --> 00:40:29,919
Is his life more precious than our lives?

562
00:40:29,919 --> 00:40:32,359
Magistrate Hu,
you've always loved the people like sons.

563
00:40:32,359 --> 00:40:35,959
Are you just going to watch this man
die in front of you?

564
00:40:35,959 --> 00:40:36,959
T-Trade!

565
00:40:36,959 --> 00:40:38,399
- Make the trade!
- Make the trade!

566
00:40:38,399 --> 00:40:41,502
Make the trade!

567
00:40:56,400 --> 00:41:00,520
I cannot watch any Wanshan people
die before my eyes.

568
00:41:00,520 --> 00:41:04,120
But Zhao Zheng De is a key witness
Lord Zhan must protect.

569
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:05,680
I cannot send him to his death either.

570
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:07,040
Weighing the two options,

571
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:08,760
it is a difficult choice.

572
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,600
Therefore, as for the hostage...

573
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,839
I will take his place.

574
00:41:11,839 --> 00:41:14,590
You mustn't, Your Honor.

575
00:41:16,479 --> 00:41:18,760
Zhu Ming Yuan. I severed my own arm.

576
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:20,680
I will be your hostage. How about it?

577
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:25,150
- Don't come over!
- Release him. I will be your hostage.

578
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:28,662
My dear!

579
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:34,920
My dear!

580
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:38,160
My dear!

581
00:41:38,160 --> 00:41:40,400
My dear!

582
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:44,402
My dear!

583
00:41:50,802 --> 00:41:51,840
Brother.

584
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:53,600
Ling Long.

585
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:39,167
Ma'am.

586
00:42:42,439 --> 00:42:45,040
I am sorry, ma'am. I failed to save him.

587
00:42:45,040 --> 00:42:46,560
It's all right, Lord Hu.

588
00:42:46,560 --> 00:42:50,937
You have done your best today.
